movie_title: Star Wars: Episode I - The Phantom Menace
title: Too good to talk about
review: I must say that this movie was so great that I'm even having trouble commenting on it!!!  This movie deserves to take over Titanic's spot as the #1 highest grossing movie to ever hit the box office.  I've seen it seven times and I'm planning on seeing it again.  I suggest all of you IMDb users do the same.
